Hi Team,
Starting a discussion on productionizing frontend observability. This will require effort from both the frontend and infra sides. In terms of bandwidth allocation for the infra work, we have someone joining the team in a few weeks who could help with this work. Does that timeline align with what we need for productionizing frontend observability?
Additionally, in terms of scope in Q4, do we want to focus on enabling frontend observability specifically for AIHub, or should we aim to cover all SaaS tenants?

Looking forward to your thoughts! c.c. @Serena @lydia @sudeep
hey @abhitaker thanks for sending this. Also discussing the priority / timelines with eng Lydia and Kerry, will keep you all posted
